xxl.core.math.statistics.nonparametric.kernels

Class TriweightKernel

  • java.lang.Object
    • xxl.core.math.statistics.nonparametric.kernels.KernelFunction
      • xxl.core.math.statistics.nonparametric.kernels.TriweightKernel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Differentiable, Integrable, RealFunction

    public class TriweightKernel
extends KernelFunction
implements Integrable, Differentiable
    This class models the Triweight kernel function. Thus, it extends KernelFunction. Since the primitive is known, this class also implements Integrable.
    See Also:
    KernelFunction, Kernels, KernelFunctionND, KernelBandwidths
